### Real Time DevOps Project | Deploy to Kubernetes Using Jenkins | End to End DevOps Project | CICD

- Building a complete CICD Pipeline using Jenkins, Mavern, Docker and EKS
- If developer makes any changes to the application repostory on GitHub, it triggers the CI job of Jenkins
- Pushes the code from the application repository, builds and tests the artifacts using Mavern
- Do the static code analytics of the artifacts using SonarQube
- Build the Docker image, push the docker image to docker hub
- Scan the Docker image using Trivy Scan
- Our CD job starts 
- updates the build number or release number of the manifest deployment yaml files on the Git Ops repository
- ArgoCD will pull the updated manifest file and deploy the resources to EKS Cluster
- A notification will be send to Slack channel

